Testing Activities for Dark Mode Feature (Spotify)

1. Test Planning
- Role: Test Leader
- Create the test plan for the Dark Mode feature.

2. Test Case Design
- Role: Tester
- Write test cases to verify Dark Mode functionality.

3. Test Execution
- Role: Tester
- Test whether Dark Mode works correctly on different screens.

4. Bug Reporting
- Role: Tester
- Report any issues found during testing.

5. Test Review
- Role: Test Leader
- Review test results and approve the feature for release.